stages.name: Publishing
stages.content:
1. Revise and ensure job name and video name are in the same format: use case ({target audience})
  2. Add tag "Unlisted"
  3. Set "Recommended playback speed" to 1.0x or 1.2x
  4. Share link, starting at 0:00
  5. Open the shared link in incognito mode to review 1 last time
  6. Move job to next stage "Monitoring performance"
  7. Promote your own products
